VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (CryptoJS\.DES\.encrypt|MD5|SHA-1|RC4)\(.+\)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:crypto\.subtle|node:crypto|webcrypto|bcrypt|argon2|scrypt && MISSING:test|example|spec|checksum|integrity
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of weak cryptographic functions.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Weak Cryptography.
